reviewText: No one presents detailed information as well as Shihan Annesi. This set should be required study for any serious student of aiki, aiki jujutsu, aikido or any other Okinawan/Japanese martial art. The basics are clearly explained, and the techniques illustrating these basics are a continuing source of information in developing practical self defense. If you want to learn a martial art or improve your martial art, this is a set you should acquire!!!
